img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜畀人話我咁做好on9<br />\n利申a0 如果有機會約到女仔出街實會帶佢去博物館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以你咪無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸:無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪因爲你太悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實去博物館唔on9<br />\n睇下你點樣將佢變得有趣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fff614b41817c95e5bafda07279356a338f242c","tid":22653,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"機鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaa10501b52b743f636737da800b15e6cab82c4","tid":22653,"uid":9987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會上網睇近期有乜好食 跟住周圍食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢會話行到好攰<br />\n其實我都幾中意咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日拉住佢周圍去食 我覺得西灣河 深水埗 葵芳都幾多正野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n葵芳我地成間商場食過咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深水埗少入可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西九都幾正 有得坐 附近都仲有好多小食 唔洗行太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5620abd59c218e0bb51a9462af0684fd57fed2","tid":22653,"uid":1286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果去博物館又點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那有女，你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去博物館都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜畀人話我咁做好on9<br />\n利申a0 如果有機會約到女仔出街實會帶佢去博物館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以你咪無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸:無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪因爲你太悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實去博物館唔on9<br />\n睇下你點樣將佢變得有趣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實去博物館幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平平地買張半年票<br />\n玩博物館一日遊<br />\n淨係尖沙咀果4個都夠行一日<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就入大棠影紅葉<br />\n或者入下長洲大澳行下<br />\n沙田踩下單車又得"},{"pid":"3965809c3b2386dbfcc02435f1df5e4366f6fb61","tid":22653,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果去博物館又點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那有女，你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去博物館都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜畀人話我咁做好on9<br />\n利申a0 如果有機會約到女仔出街實會帶佢去博物館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以你咪無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸:無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪因爲你太悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實去博物館唔on9<br />\n睇下你點樣將佢變得有趣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個女仔係鍾意你嘅就算你唔講嘢，兩個人一齊感受下對方嘅傳在都可以好冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad0c8313f652f79d5a4b5020ebcc067d7d2f471","tid":22653,"uid":2368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:27: